text: "Nobody exists on purpose. Nobody belongs anywhere. We are all going to die. Come watch TV."
"Weddings are basically funerals with a cake."
"Listen, Morty, I hate to break it to you, but what people call 'love' is just a chemical reaction that compels animals to breed."
"I'm sorry, but your opinion means very little to me."
"I'm a scientist; because I invent, transform, create, and destroy for a living, and when I don't like something about the world, I change it."
"Sometimes Science Is More Art Than Science!"
"Honey, stop raising your father's cholesterol so you can take a hot funeral selfie"
"Before what you're trying to do was called negging, it was called reverse psychology, and incels didn't invent it, Bugs Bunny did"
"He's not a hot girl. He can't just bail on his life and set up shop in someone else's."
"Excuse me. Coming through. What are you here for? Just kidding, I don't care."
"The world is full of idiots who don't understand what's important! And they'll try to tear us apart, Morty!"
"Don't get drawn into the culture, Morty. Stealing stuff is about the stuff, not the stealing."
"Don't do it guys! The casualties would be in the brazillions. Cause you're Brazilian? It's a threat and a pun! Nobody gets me."
"It's like the N word and the C word had a baby and it was raised by all the bad words for Jews."
